Derived components:
  - src/middleware/policyEngine.js
      Policy-priority evaluation engine (Block > Manual Approval > Rate Limit > Allow),
      per-token rule matching, and sliding-window rate limit counters.
      Derived from: apps/gateway/src/policy.rs

  - src/routes/policy.js
      Per-request manual approval workflow (pending approvals, long-poll, approve/deny).
      Derived from: apps/gateway/src/approval.rs

  - src/gateway/tokens.js (namespace prefix pattern)
      "oc_"-style namespaced token prefix for fast rejection before DB lookup.
      Derived from: apps/web/src/lib/validate-api-key.ts

  - src/database.js (HMAC OAuth state)
      HMAC-SHA256 signed OAuth state tokens with timingSafeEqual verification.
      Derived from: apps/web/src/lib/oauth-state.ts

